Junior Bake Off: Episode 1
Four junior bakers try to follow a surprise recipe for strawberry shortcake stacks.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 2
Four junior bakers follow a classic French recipe for patisserie madeleines.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 3
Four junior bakers attempt to create a show-stopping vegetable cake.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 4
Four junior bakers attempt to create rotis - flatbreads spiced with cumin and turmeric.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 5
Four junior bakers attempt to create a salted caramel cake.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 6
Alice, Corey, Finlay and Sufia attempt to bake their dream birthday cake.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 7
Alfie, Andrea, Freddie and Lucy attempt a rustic cheese soda bread.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 8
Ben, Darcey, Isabel and Will try to depict their lives in biscuit form.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 9
Amari, Ben, Khushi and Oscar attempt an old-fashioned jam roly-poly.

Junior Bake Off: Episode 10
Ben, Grace, Purdey and Tom attempt to produce iced ring doughnuts.

Junior Bake Off: 11. Quarter Final 1
The first five quarter-finalists enter the tent.

Junior Bake Off: 12. Quarter Final 2
The second batch of quarter-finalists attempt show-stopping mini tarts.

Junior Bake Off: 13. The Semi-Final
It's the semi-final, and the bakers attempt bread buns in the shapes of animals.

Junior Bake Off: 14. The Final - Day 1
It's the final and the last four bakers attempt rough-puff pastry pinwheel pastries.

Junior Bake Off: 15. The Final - Day 2
The four finalists face the final challenge - creating a tiered and layered cake
